There are five key elements in great games.

Game Characters.
JUST YOU

Goals.
EARN POINTS BY HITTING A BLOCK

Decisions.
HIT BALL AS MANY TIMES

Rewards.
HIGH SCORE

Immersion and Presence
QUICK REACTIONS TRY NOT TO MISS THE BALL

Player starts the game with 3 lives
The player loses a game if his live total decreases to 0
A life is removed every time the player misses the ball
